
String:
======

1. Write a program to print the given string in reverse order.

2. Write a program for the following scenario.
String companyName="XTGLOBAL INFOTECH LIMITED";
i. Print the total number of characters in the string
ii. Combine two strings and print it on the console.
iii. Print the character at the index 3.

3. Write a program to split the string with comma separator and print all string elements on the console.
String countries="India,South Africa,Australia,China,Pakistan,USA";